ass=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>고양이<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">[disabled]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> gray<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">[data-cute-animal]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pink<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>[ABC]</strong><br />\n속성 ABC 를 포함한 요소를 선택한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-attrvalue\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-attrvalue\" aria-label=\"2 attrvalue permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. [attr=“value”]</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">[type='text']</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pink<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>[ABC=“XYZ”]</strong><br />\n속성 ABC 를 포함하면서 값이 XYZ 인 요소를 선택한다.</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%EC%9E%90-attribute-selector\">💙 속성 선택자 (Attribute Selector)</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-attr\">1. [attr]</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-attrvalue\">2. [attr=“value”]</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"2022.03.09","title":"[CSS] 속성 선택자","categories":"CSS","author":"안가을","emoji":null},"fields":{"slug":"/css/attribute-selector/"}},"prev":{"id":"74d27a26-e046-5d53-b2b5-31474c5803e1","html":"<h2 id=\"-선택자-우선순위\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%EC%9E%90-%EC%9A%B0%EC%84%A0%EC%88%9C%EC%9C%84\" aria-label=\" 선택자 우선순위 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💙 선택자 우선순위</h2>\n<br />\n<p>우선순위란, 같은 요소가 여러 선언의 대상이 된 경우,<br />\n어떤 선언의 <strong>CSS 속성을 우선적으로 적용</strong>할 지 결정하는 방법이다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">1</code> <strong>점수</strong>가 높은 선언의 우선순위가 높다.<br />\n<code class=\"language-text\">2</code> 점수가 같다면, 가장 <strong>마지막에 해석</strong>된 (나중에 작성된) 선언의 우선순위가 높다.<br /></p>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"1-점수가-높은-선언의-우선순위가-높다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EC%A0%90%EC%88%98%EA%B0%80-%EB%86%92%EC%9D%80-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8%EC%9D%98-%EC%9A%B0%EC%84%A0%EC%88%9C%EC%9C%84%EA%B0%80-%EB%86%92%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"1 점수가 높은 선언의 우선순위가 높다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 점수가 높은 선언의 우선순위가 높다.</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>color_yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">'</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>color_green<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Inline style 선언 --></span>\n  Hello, world!\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red <span class=\"token important\">!important</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#color_yellow</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.color_green</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> green<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">*</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> darkblue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> violet<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> // 글자 속성 => 상속 가능\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<br />\n<p>각 CSS 선택자에 예를 든 점수별로 순위를 매겨보면 아래와 같다.<br />\n(CSS 우선순위의 점수를 계산하는 것을 명시도라고 부른다.)</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">1</code> <strong>important</strong> (9999999999점)<br />\n<code class=\"language-text\">2</code> <strong>Inline</strong> style 선언 (1000점)<br />\n<code class=\"language-text\">3</code> <strong>ID</strong> 선택자 (100점)<br />\n<code class=\"language-text\">4</code> <strong>Class</strong> 선택자 (10점)<br />\n<code class=\"language-text\">5</code> <strong>Tag</strong> 선택자 (1점)<br />\n<code class=\"language-text\">6</code> <strong>*(전체)</strong> 선택자 (0점)<br />\n<code class=\"language-text\">7</code> 상속 => 상속이 가능하지만 별도로 점수를 계산하지 않음<br /></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>따라서 위의 코드에서는 !important 키워드를 사용한 red 컬러의 색상이 적용된다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br />\n<h4 id=\"우선순위-점수-계산-예시\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9A%B0%EC%84%A0%EC%88%9C%EC%9C%84-%EC%A0%90%EC%88%98-%EA%B3%84%EC%82%B0-%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\" aria-label=\"우선순위 점수 계산 예시 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[우선순위 점수 계산 예시]</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.list li.item</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Class + Tag + Class<br />\n10 + 1 + 10 = 21 점</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.list li:hover</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Class + Tag + Class<br />\n10 + 1 + 10 = 21 점<br />\nhover => 가상 클래스! 선택자</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.box::before</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Class + Tag<br />\n10 + 1 = 11 점<br />\nbefore => 가상 요소! 선택자 => 태그 선택자<br />\n요소와 태그는 다른 개념이긴 하지만 혼용해서도 많이 부른다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">#submit span</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ID + Tag<br />\n100 + 1 = 101 점</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">header .menu li:nth-child(2)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Tag + Class + Tag + Class<br />\n1 + 10 + 1 + 10 = 22 점</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">h1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Tag<br />\n1 점</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">:not(.box)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Class (.box)<br />\n10 점 <br />\nnot 은 해당 요소를 부정하는 것이기 때문에<br />\n가상 클래스! 선택자이긴 하지만, 점수로 계산하지 않는다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"2-점수가-같다면-가장-마지막에-작성된-선언의-우선순위가-높다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%A0%90%EC%88%98%EA%B0%80-%EA%B0%99%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4-%EA%B0%80%EC%9E%A5-%EB%A7%88%EC%A7%80%EB%A7%89%EC%97%90-%EC%9E%91%EC%84%B1%EB%90%9C-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8%EC%9D%98-%EC%9A%B0%EC%84%A0%EC%88%9C%EC%9C%84%EA%B0%80-%EB%86%92%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"2 점수가 같다면 가장 마지막에 작성된 선언의 우선순위가 높다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 점수가 같다면, 가장 마지막에 작성된 선언의 우선순위가 높다.</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.hello</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.hello</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>선택자가 같다 == 점수가 같다.<br />\n이 경우, 가장 마지막에 작성된 orange 색상이 적용된다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">div.hello</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.hello</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>.hello 선택자가 더 마지막에 작성되었더라도,<br />\ndiv.hello 선택자의 점수가 더 높기 때문에 yellow 색상이 적용된다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"3-inline-style-과-important\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-inline-style-%EA%B3%BC-important\" aria-label=\"3 inline style 과 important permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Inline Style 과 !important</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">1</code> Inline style<br />\n별도의 CSS 파일에서 수정이 불가능하고<br />\n수정을 하기 위해서 해당 코드를 직접 찾아야 하기 때문에, <br />\n되도록 사용하지 않는 것이 좋다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">2</code> !important<br />\n!important 가 적용된 스타일을 다른 방식으로 수정하는 것은 불가능하다.<br />\n결국 또 다시 !important 를 추가하게 되기 때문에, 되도록 사용하지 않는 것이 좋다.</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%EC%9E%90-%EC%9A%B0%EC%84%A0%EC%88%9C%EC%9C%84\">💙 선택자 우선순위</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#1-%EC%A0%90%EC%88%98%EA%B0%80-%EB%86%92%EC%9D%80-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8%EC%9D%98-%EC%9A%B0%EC%84%A0%EC%88%9C%EC%9C%84%EA%B0%80-%EB%86%92%EB%8B%A4\">1. 점수가 높은 선언의 우선순위가 높다.</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%9A%B0%EC%84%A0%EC%88%9C%EC%9C%84-%EC%A0%90%EC%88%98-%EA%B3%84%EC%82%B0-%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\">[우선순위 점수 계산 예시]</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-%EC%A0%90%EC%88%98%EA%B0%80-%EA%B0%99%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4-%EA%B0%80%EC%9E%A5-%EB%A7%88%EC%A7%80%EB%A7%89%EC%97%90-%EC%9E%91%EC%84%B1%EB%90%9C-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8%EC%9D%98-%EC%9A%B0%EC%84%A0%EC%88%9C%EC%9C%84%EA%B0%80-%EB%86%92%EB%8B%A4\">2. 점수가 같다면, 가장 마지막에 작성된 선언의 우선순위가 높다.</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#3-inline-style-%EA%B3%BC-important\">3. Inline Style 과 !important</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"2022.03.09","title":"[CSS] 선택자 우선순위","categories":"CSS","author":"안가을","emoji":null},"fields":{"slug":"/css/selector-priority/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://autumnly1007.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":"autumnly1007/autumnly1007.github.io"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/css/style-inherit/","nextSlug":"/css/attribute-selector/","prevSlug":"/css/selector-priority/"}},
    "staticQueryHashes": ["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"]}